        "realDate": "2026-07-17",
        "notes": "Party helped Prof. Mizzix to clear the house. He'll study resonance abnormalities for 7 days.Party owns own a bastion. Granted the bastion’s meditation-room benefit: advantage on Charisma saving throws until the next long rest after a rest there.Friendly toward Nico after the Red Wastes performance. Wants to recruit him for a future spectacle.",
        "sessionLog": "<strong>Session 1 — Blind Pit</strong><br><br>The party participated in the illegal fights at the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"f9o4ryw59F9BHk0P\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.f9o4ryw59F9BHk0P\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Blind Pit</span>&nbsp; when a mysterious explosion orchestrated by the Rakdos went off while <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"xrpg5csrfyF8bkoy\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.xrpg5csrfyF8bkoy\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Lavinia of the Tenth</span>&nbsp;was raiding the place, destroying the arena.&nbsp;<br><br>During the chaos they recovered:<br><br>The unconscious Dimir agent <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"KtUG0Wlb74NQH5B7\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.KtUG0Wlb74NQH5B7\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Sable, Dimir Informant</span>&nbsp;<br>An <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Orzhov Crystal</span>&nbsp;<br><br>Escaping through the sewers, they were intercepted by mysterious flying <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"pEa04U6tcWbTxsAh\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.pEa04U6tcWbTxsAh\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Thopter</span>, monitored by Lazav",
