        "notes": "",
        "sessionLog": "Session 2 — Loose Ends<br><br>The party destroyed the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"pEa04U6tcWbTxsAh\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.pEa04U6tcWbTxsAh\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Thopter</span>&nbsp;<br><br><span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"KtUG0Wlb74NQH5B7\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.KtUG0Wlb74NQH5B7\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Sable, Dimir Informant</span>&nbsp;regained consciousness and revealed that several factions were searching for the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Orzhov Crystal</span>&nbsp;. She hid at the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"SOlKba3PwfoEZbwU\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.SOlKba3PwfoEZbwU\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Edgewall Small Tavern</span>&nbsp;, asking the party to decide whether they would return it to her superior, Vethis.<br><br>While considering their options, they accepted a job from <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"TVmFW8umyCeSrLNd\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.TVmFW8umyCeSrLNd\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Guttersnipe</span>&nbsp;to investigate a <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"ZlPePvYVO9ejGr53\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.ZlPePvYVO9ejGr53\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Simic Warehouse</span>&nbsp;.<br><br>The mission went terribly.<br><br>The party fled...<br><br>...leaving dangerous Simic creatures loose in the district.<br><br>The consequences would return later.",
