        "sessionLog": "Session 4 — Return to the Blind Pit<br><br><span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"dhIK2PsfHdmJn8Yd\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.dhIK2PsfHdmJn8Yd\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Vesk</span>&nbsp;, <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"o73oz4VuacTw0uff\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.o73oz4VuacTw0uff\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Babar, The Bonded</span>&nbsp;'s handler, finally contacted the party.<br><br>He entrusted Babar with a mysterious access card and tasked the group with recovering the remaining <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"zB4aEsIYw4OKeKl0\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.zB4aEsIYw4OKeKl0\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Powerstone Shard</span>&nbsp;from the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"kgJwooRvH1DrQkOz\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.kgJwooRvH1DrQkOz\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Blind Pit destroyed</span>&nbsp; before anyone else could.<br><br>The mission succeeded.<br><br>The party escaped after triggering another explosion that destroyed what little remained of the site.<br><br>Meanwhile...<br><br><span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Jace Beleren</span>&nbsp; psychically contacted <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"X8f1ZeHs0klsZyrR\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.X8f1ZeHs0klsZyrR\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Nico-Lahz</span>&nbsp;, asking him to meet privately.",
