        "notes": "",
        "sessionLog": "Session 5 — The Mask of Memory<br>The party met <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Jace Beleren</span>&nbsp;beneath <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"6k87ArLSEfVp9IVj\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.6k87ArLSEfVp9IVj\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Vitu Gazi</span>&nbsp;<br>Jace explained that someone appeared to be rewriting Ravnica's memories and feared a conspiracy beyond his understanding.<br>He asked the party to retrieve an ancient artifact:<br>The <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Mask Of Memory</span>&nbsp;<br>The trail led to <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"9fWZpu7fUJqA7yaO\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.9fWZpu7fUJqA7yaO\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Karn's Bastion</span>&nbsp;<br>The party recovered the Mask...<br>...and that night entered a shared nightmare.<br>Inside they confronted their deepest fears before facing <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"6vfZ9m46zw952cCP\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.6vfZ9m46zw952cCP\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Sheoldred the Apocalypse</span>&nbsp;, an entity that could not be defeated. They died to it, to wake up close to the mask. Just a nightmare.",
