        "notes": "",
        "sessionLog": "Session 6 — The Karlov Maze<br><br>The party returned the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Mask Of Memory</span>&nbsp;to <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.5dGMmVmcIkbEs9tA\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Jace Beleren</span>&nbsp;.<br><br>Unable to explain what had happened, Jace directed them toward <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"cZIkCCPhzzLdBpM2\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.cZIkCCPhzzLdBpM2\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Agata Karlov</span>&nbsp;, believing she might understand the artifact.<br><br>Their search led into the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"2GiF5upVge11U1nK\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.2GiF5upVge11U1nK\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Karlov Maze</span>&nbsp;<br><br>Subtlety lasted only briefly.<br><br>The maze caught fire.<br><br>The Orzhov responded immediately.<br><br>The party was overwhelmed, captured and imprisoned.",
