        "notes": "",
        "sessionLog": "Session 7 — Judgment<br>The party awoke inside <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"scene\" data-mention-id=\"P3Lmxz8VIo4gcUwQ\" data-mention-uuid=\"Scene.P3Lmxz8VIo4gcUwQ\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Karlov Manor</span>&nbsp;<br><span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"XBhoiGincckXCmik\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.XBhoiGincckXCmik\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Teysa Karlov</span>&nbsp; personally interrogated them before confiscating all of their possessions, including the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Mask Of Memory</span>&nbsp;, <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.JXAj1bY05R1LfpKG\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Orzhov Crystal</span>&nbsp;, <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"j42m3XOmgi4b87I0\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.j42m3XOmgi4b87I0\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Mysterious Access Card</span>&nbsp;, <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"zB4aEsIYw4OKeKl0\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.zB4aEsIYw4OKeKl0\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Powerstone Shard</span>&nbsp;.<br><span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"cZIkCCPhzzLdBpM2\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.cZIkCCPhzzLdBpM2\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Agata Karlov</span>&nbsp;revealed she recognized the Mask immediately.<br>She warned that Teysa intended to weaponize it.<br>During the interrogation, <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"actor\" data-mention-id=\"dhIK2PsfHdmJn8Yd\" data-mention-uuid=\"Actor.dhIK2PsfHdmJn8Yd\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Vesk</span>&nbsp;appeared.<br>Disappointed by the party's repeated failures, he branded them with five Debt Tokens, effectively placing them under Dimir probation.<br>After escaping confinement, the party infiltrated Orzhov holdings, defeated the guards, reclaimed the <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.NMfH7unhwbBMIbpL\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Mask Of Memory</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;and fled Karlov Manor.<br>On the streets afterward...<br>Frikka discovered an odd prototype.<br>The now-infamous <span class=\"nd-mention\" data-nd-mention=\"\" data-mention-kind=\"item\" data-mention-id=\"EbxszjT0ryXS3P9a\" data-mention-uuid=\"Item.EbxszjT0ryXS3P9a\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Izzet Shitty Device</span>&nbsp;",
